These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, soccer, ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | soy-milk    | almond-milk    | sprite |
| Sport      | swimming | skiing | ice-hockey | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, cola, coffee
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, broccoli, cauliflower, corn
1. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
3. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
4. the person drinking juice is not the person eating broccoli##6
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice  | cola    | tea | coffee    |
| Food       | corn | broccoli | cauliflower  | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, coffee, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, musician, dressmaker, paramedic
1. the person drinking lemonade is not the security-guard##6
2. the musician is not the person drinking coffee##6
3. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
4. the musician is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the musician##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
7. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
8. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade       | mirinda  | almond-milk  | coffee |
| Job        | dressmaker | paramedic | musician | security-guard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, dog, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, motorbike, airplane, roller
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
3. the person driving the roller is not the owner of the hamster##6
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | hamster | dog | goat     | mouse |
| Transport   | motorbike     | airplane    | taxi | roller    |

