.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, tea, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, ship, taxi, quad-bike
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
5. the person driving the tram is not the person drinking coffee##6
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee        | mirinda | tea | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | quad-bike | tram | ship     | taxi   |

