.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, satire, zombie, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, brazilian, spanish, italian
1. the nigerian is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is not the brazilian##6
3. the nigerian is on the far right##1
4. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
5. the person watching zombie movies is the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
8. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
9. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the italian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | zombie    | scientific  | sports   |
| Nationality   | spanish  | italian | brazilian | nigerian |

