.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, drama, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, dubstep, blues, rock
1. the fan blues is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
2. the fan blues is not the person watching scientific movies##6
3. the person watching animation movies is the fan dubstep##1
4. the fan folk is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
5. the fan blues is on the far left##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the fan folk##1
7. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific     | drama | animation |
| Music-Genre   | blues | folk | rock      | dubstep         |

