.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, cola, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, nurse, scientist, librarian
1. the doctor is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
3. the librarian is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the nurse is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the nurse##3
6. the doctor is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is not the librarian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | water        | cola      | coffee          |
| Job        | doctor | nurse | librarian | scientist |

