.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, analyst, doctor, chef
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, bus, jet-ski, bike
1. the coach is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is not the chef##6
3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person driving the bike is the doctor##1
7. the coach is not the person driving the bike##6
8. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the chef##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | coach  | doctor | chef    | analyst |
| Transport   | bus | bike | jet-ski | trike  |

