.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, chinchilla, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, rugby, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is basketball is not the owner of the lizard##6
2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
6. the person who's sport is rowing is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | chinchilla | lizard        | goat  | dog     |
| Sport   | basketball     | lacrosse | rowing | rugby |

