.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, sudoku, gardening, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, reggae, country, r&b
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the fan reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
3. the fan country is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the fan reggae is between the fan blues and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | gardening | sudoku    | hiking | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | reggae | r&b   | country     |

