.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, subway, boat
1. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
2. the person eating pomegranate is not the person driving the airplane##6
3. the person driving the tram is the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
5. the person driving the subway is not the person eating pomegranate##6
6. the person eating broccoli is not the person driving the airplane##6
7. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person eating broccoli##5
8. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | nectarine  | lime | broccoli | pomegranate |
| Transport   | subway | airplane     | boat     | tram    |

