.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, kale, zucchini, garlic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, thriller, superhero
1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
2. the person eating kale is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
3. the person eating peach is the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
5. the person eating peach is between the person eating kale and the person watching sports movies##2
6. the person eating kale is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | garlic | kale      | peach | zucchini   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | thriller | superhero   | sports |

