3. the person watching spy movies is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice | mirinda     | sprite     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | satire       | spy | drama |

