2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is not the person drinking sprite##6
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
6. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | sprite | milk | 7up      | fanta   |
| Transport   | van  | boat   | tram | motorbike |

 